quran[50]{c,v,t}:
  77,1,Ngifunga ngokuthunyelwe ngokudedelana
  77,2,Ngifunga nangemimoya evunguza ngodlame
  77,3,Ngifunga kanye nemimoya esakazayo
  77,4,Ngifunga nangomoya osakazayo
  77,5,Ngifunga nangemimoya ekhumbuzayo
  77,6,Izaba noma ukuxwayisa
  77,7,Ngempela lokho enethenjiswa kona kuzokwenzeka
  77,8,Khumbula lapho izinkanyezi zifiphaliswa (ukukhanya kwazo)
  77,9,Futhi khumbula ngenkathi izulu lidatshulwa phakathi
  77,10,Futhi khumbula ngenkathi izintaba zisuswa
  77,11,Khumbula nangenkathi izithunywa ziqoqwa ngesikhathi (esibekiwe)
  77,12,Kuhlehliselwe luphi usuku
  77,13,Usuku lokwahlulela
  77,14,Futhi yini ekwenza ukuthi wazi ukuthi luyini usuku lokwahlulela
  77,15,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphika (iqiniso)
  77,16,Asizange yini sibabhubhise abasendulo
  77,17,Bese sibalandelanise ngabokugcina
  77,18,Senza kanjalo ngezigebengu (labo abanecala)
  77,19,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,20,Asizange yini sinidale ngamanzi anyanyekayo
  77,21,Ngakho-ke sawabeka endaweni ephephile
  77,22,Kuze kube yisikhathi esaziwayo
  77,23,Ngakho-ke sanquma futhi singabanqumi abahle kakhulu
  77,24,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,25,Asizange yini siwenze umhlaba ukuthi ube wumbuthela (kuwo na)
  77,26,Okuphilayo nokufileyo
  77,27,Futhi sabeka kuwona izintaba eziphakeme futhi saniphuzisa amanzi amtoti
  77,28,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,29,Hambani niye kulokho enanikuphika
  77,30,Hambani niye ethunzini elinezigaba ezintathu
  77,31,Alikho ithunzi (alisithi ithunzi) futhi alisizi ekubhekaneni nelangabi (lomlilo)
  77,32,Ngempela lona likhipha izinhlansi (ezinkulu) njengendlu enkulu eyinqaba
  77,33,Okusengathi ngamakameli aphuzi
  77,34,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,35,Lolu wusuku abayobe bengakhulumi ngalo
  77,36,Futhi angeke banikezwe imvume yokuthi benze izaba
  77,37,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,38,"Lolu wusuku lokwahlulela, siniqoqile kanye nabasendulu"
  77,39,Ngakho-ke uma ninecebo lenzeni ukubhekana nami
  77,40,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,41,"Ngempela\tabesabayo\t(abalungileyo)\tbasemithunzini nasemithonjeni"
  77,42,Nasezithelweni kulezo abazifisayo
  77,43,Yidlani futhi niphuze (ngokuzanelisa) nangentokozo ngenxa yalokho enanikwenza
  77,44,"Ngempela, kanjalo sibanika umvuzo abenzi bokuhle"
  77,45,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,46,"Yidlani\tnizithokozise\tokwesikhashana\tngempela\tnina niyizigebengu"
  77,47,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,48,"Futhi uma kuthiwa kubona, “khothamani” abakhothami"
  77,49,Usizi ngalolosuku kwabaphikayo
  77,50,Ngakho-ke iyiphi inkulumo abayoyikholwa emva kwayo